{
  "name": "RPlog_Healing_on_Calamari",
  "title": "A Bedside Confession on Mon Calamari",
  "summary": "Recovering in a Calamari hospital with his injured right arm sealed in a bacta enclosure awaiting a new prosthetic, Luke Skywalker is visited by Jessalyn, who comes to thank him for rescuing her, and shortly after by his sister Leia. After Leia leaves to attend diplomatic matters and pass along word of their safe arrival, Luke gently presses Jessalyn about her awkwardness around him, drawing out the subject of the kiss they shared. Jessalyn admits she is in love with him, while Luke, pained, confesses he cannot pursue a relationship given his responsibilities, even as the two share tender kisses and admissions of feeling. The conversation ends unresolved but affectionate, with Jessalyn promising to return the next day as Luke settles back to rest. The log is an intimate, dialogue-driven character piece centered on the strained romance between Luke and Jessalyn.",
